description: Apt. is very conveniently located a few blocks from almost every subway line (N,Q, R, 4, 5, 6, F). It is right by Central Park, museums, Bloomingdales, lots of great restaurants, Whole Foods, manicure + pedicure places, salons, the Plaza Hotel, Madison Ave., Park Ave., Fifth Ave., etc. It is good for solo adventurers and business travelers. No guests please. The building is on a very quiet, tree-lined street of private homes. It has a doorman Monday through Friday 7am-11pm and a laundry room.
name: Beautiful, Spacious Studio In VERY Convenient Area
review: The host canceled this reservation 6 days before arrival. This is an automated posting.
